<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Event Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #f59e0b; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #fffbeb; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .event-details { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #666; }
        .reminder { background: #fef3c7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; margin: 20px 0; }
        .countdown { text-align: center; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #f59e0b; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>⏰ Event Reminder</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
        
        <div class="reminder">
            <p><strong>Don't forget!</strong> Your registered event <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong> is coming up soon.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="countdown">
            🕐 Tomorrow!
        </div>
        
        <div class="event-details">
            <h3>📅 Event Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Event:</strong> {{eventTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{eventDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{eventLocation}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>Preparation checklist:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>✅ Mark your calendar</li>
            <li>✅ Plan your transportation</li>
            <li>✅ Prepare any required materials</li>
            <li>✅ Bring a valid ID for check-in</li>
            <li>✅ Arrive 15 minutes early</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>We're excited to see you at the event! If you have any questions or need to make changes to your registration, please contact us.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Need to cancel?</strong> Please let us know as soon as possible so we can offer your spot to someone on the waitlist.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,<br>The One Event Team</p>
        <p><small>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</small></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
